## Checklist 2: File Permissions & Path Security

### 2.1 SharedPreferences
- [ ] NO `chmod 666` on SharedPreferences XML files
- [ ] `fixPermissions()` uses `setReadable(true, true)` = owner-only
- [ ] Root fallback uses `chmod 600` with `canonicalPath` symbol-link guard
- [ ] `commit()` replaced with `apply()` to avoid sync IO block
- [ ] 30+ field single-transaction writes reviewed for split potential

### 2.2 Temporary / External Files
- [ ] NO config mirror to `/data/local/tmp/` (global readable)
- [ ] Ephemeris/rinex files in `context.filesDir` (private), NOT `/data/local/tmp/`
- [ ] `copyTo` followed immediately by `setReadable`/`setWritable` (permission window)
- [ ] Step counter persistence uses `chmod 600`, not `666`

### 2.3 Native Library Loading (TOCTOU)
- [ ] SO loaded from system-protected `nativeLibraryDir`, NOT `/data/local/tmp/`
- [ ] Random file names (`libkys_*.so` pattern)
- [ ] `canonicalPath` symbol-link TOCTOU guard before `System.load()`
- [ ] `load_library` remote command explicitly disabled
- [ ] SHA-256 integrity check on loaded SO (optional but recommended)

### 2.4 Backup & Data Extraction
- [ ] `backup_rules.xml` excludes `sharedpref` and `database` domains
- [ ] `data_extraction_rules.xml` same exclusion
- [ ] `allowBackup` is `false` OR exclusion rules verified effective

