## Checklist 8: Build & Supply Chain

### 8.1 Build Configuration
- [ ] `kotlin-serialization` plugin version matches compiler version
- [ ] NO hardcoded `org.gradle.java.home` absolute path
- [ ] AGP public API used (not `BaseVariantOutputImpl` internal class)
- [ ] ProGuard rules for all modules
- [ ] Native targets: `-fvisibility=hidden`, `-Wl,--strip-all`, FULL RELRO

### 8.2 Dependencies
- [ ] fastjson2 version checked against OSV database (known DoS CVEs)
- [ ] OkHttp: certificate pinning for critical endpoints (ephemeris download)
- [ ] Dobby: version locked to specific commit hash (not floating `1.2`)
- [ ] `usesCleartextTraffic` reviewed; `network_security_config.xml` preferred

### 8.3 Secrets Management
- [ ] NO hardcoded API keys in source (Baidu Map key)
- [ ] `.env` gitignored AND never committed to history
- [ ] `buildConfigField` from env variable for keys

