## Checklist 9: Performance Hot Paths

### 9.1 IO
- [ ] `SharedPreferences.commit()` → `apply()` (async)
- [ ] ContentProvider writes use thread pool, not `new Thread().start()`
- [ ] Watchdog polling rate reduced when mock inactive

### 9.2 Memory Allocation
- [ ] Sensor event copy uses `thread_local` buffer, not per-call heap allocation
- [ ] GNSS satellite state hot path: `Random` calls minimized
- [ ] Reflection results cached (method refs, constructor refs)
- [ ] `forEach { }` `runCatching` in dispatch loop → `for` + `try/catch`
- [ ] NMEA parsing: lazy field extraction or pre-compiled regex

### 9.3 CPU
- [ ] GaitSimulator uses cached interpolation path (not full Fourier per sample)
- [ ] `wrapPi` while-loop → modular arithmetic `((x + PI) % TWO_PI) - PI`
- [ ] Loop broadcast uses `Handler.postDelayed` or coroutine `delay()`, not raw `Thread.sleep()` loop

