## Checklist 10: Logging Hygiene

- [ ] Release build: native `LOGD`/`LOGI`/`LOGW`/`LOGE` expand to `((void)0)`
- [ ] `XposedBridge.log` detail level reduced in release (no mock status leak)
- [ ] `MockProbeLog` disabled or downgraded in release builds
- [ ] Logcat `READ_LOGS` permission exposure considered (Android <13)
- [ ] `forceLogging` dead code removed (no setter, always false)

